text: $7 for their soft serve as at end Oct 2022. I thought the taste was alright, it was familiar but I really couldn't point it to the exact thing. Wished they served it in cones though so you can get the very last bit of the ice cream and also reduce plastic usage.
Personally, the soft serve was a bit of a let down. I had expected it to be creamier. Probably will not go back for more.
